---
title: Greek-Style Pork & Zingy Feta Salad with Cherry Tomatoes & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Fresh, zesty, and full of flavour! Juicy pork flavoured with fragrant oregano is perfectly cooked and paired with a refreshing feta salad, bursting with juicy cherry tomatoes, crunchy cucumber and zingy lemon. Topped with a drizzle of creamy pesto dressing, it’s a bright and vibrant meal that’ll have you craving more!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

